{
  "stem": "18186.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They lived another lot-- not-- a little bit longer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they did it again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's why we did this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went all-- all, the whole house, the people in the house, went up-- in the attic.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were laying all through the night, hoping that the morning will come, and they will-- they will stop.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'll be finished, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They'll be finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meanwhile, this really didn't happen in our town, in my town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they-- because of-- in the morning, we were-- we heard the gestapo speaking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They spoke in-- in German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if you're not going to go-- come out, we will-- we'll find you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll shoot you on the spot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- there was shooting going around all through there, crying, and-- and killing, and shooting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we was just stuck up there in the attic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, they came to our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They opened the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they says, any Juden?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Any Juden?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is there any Jewish people there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We said nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they said, I know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where's-- where's the ladder?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Where's the ladder from the-- from to go up there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know you must be there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So finally we look down, and that was in the barn, that was like a-- and we looked up-- down.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there we saw the gestapo, two guys, I saw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember the brown uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And maybe there was more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we started-- and I and my mother stood right there, looking down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we started-- they started to put-- to move to lower the-- the ladder down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Who started to lower the ladder?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people from up-- from the-- from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for them to come up, or to us to come down rather.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
